query:
SELECT
                c.card_id,
                c.user_id,
                c.card_number,
                c.card_type,
                c.expire_date,
                c.cvv,
                c.card_provider,
                c.created_at,
                c.updated_at,
                c.deleted_at,
                COUNT(*) OVER() AS total_count
            FROM cards c
            WHERE deleted_at IS NULL
              AND ($1::TEXT IS NULL OR 
                   c.card_number ILIKE '%' || $1 || '%' OR 
                   c.card_type ILIKE '%' || $1 || '%' OR 
                   c.card_provider ILIKE '%' || $1 || '%')
            ORDER BY c.card_id
            LIMIT $2 OFFSET $3
